in a minute. Okay?

1594
01:07:46.856 --> 01:07:48.738
And remember.
it's a secret.

1595
01:07:48.818 --> 01:07:50.820
- Got it.

1596
01:07:53.102 --> 01:07:55.024
Well. I'm just hoping
he can keep a secret

1597
