01:11:18.748 --> 01:11:20.189
- Great job. buddy!

1676
01:11:20.269 --> 01:11:22.591
- Thanks. dad!

1677
01:11:22.672 --> 01:11:24.113
- So. who wants to go
hunt for presents?

1678
01:11:24.193 --> 01:11:26.996
- (kids): Me!
- (Louis): Me!

1679
01:11:28.557 --> 01:11:30.880
