01:12:00.910 --> 01:12:03.152
- Kelby is stronger
than you think.

1691
01:12:03.232 --> 01:12:05.034
He can handle this. okay?

1692
01:12:05.114 --> 01:12:06.676
- No. he can't!

1693
01:12:06.756 --> 01:12:08.397
